The paper proposes a new method for sequential recommendation using a self-attention mechanism with a probabilistic model. This work involves machine learning and natural language processing techniques, which are commonly associated with the sub-categories of cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.AI, and cs.CV.
